      <title>摩根大通指数纳入印度债券：影响</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/jpmorgan-index-inclusion-of-india-bonds-implications</link>
      <description><![CDATA[SEB 亚洲战略主管 Eugenia Victorino、ICICI Prudential Life Insurance 高级基金经理 Vidya Iyer 和 IndiaBonds.com 联合创始人兼董事 Aditi Mittal 讨论了周五将印度政府债券纳入摩根大通政府债券指数对市场和投资者意味着什么。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/jpmorgan-index-inclusion-of-india-bonds-implications</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耐克发布销售预警后股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/nike-shares-sink-after-warning-about-sales-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的运动服装公司耐克公司 (Nike Inc.) 发布了不及预期的全年业绩展望，导致其股价下跌，加剧了投资者对其运动鞋和服装需求减弱的担忧。CFRA 的 Zachary Warring 正在接受“Bloomberg The Close”的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-06-28/nike-shares-sink-after-warning-about-sales-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 28 Jun 2024 01:23:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国数据公布前油价陷入 2021 年以来最窄交易区间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-28</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国经济数据公布之前，油价维持在 2021 年以来最窄的交易区间，这可能有助于为更广泛的市场定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-june-28</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:33:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度开始纳入债券市场，将受到更多全球关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-set-for-greater-global-attention-as-bond-inclusion-begins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通公司将于周五将印度政府债券纳入其新兴市场指数，从而向更广泛的投资者开放 1.3 万亿美元的市场，印度将吸引数十亿美元的资金流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-27/india-set-for-greater-global-attention-as-bond-inclusion-begins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 23:07:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
